     H            Y.
     F** UTLR38A ***************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM:  GET MANIFEST# FROM AB#PP10 (AISIN)              *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2023.10.09                             *
     F*  FOR AISIN                                                 *
     F*------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR38A'
     F*                    PARM           $NONY   4
     F*                    PARM           $INVN  20
     F*                    PARM           $MANI  20
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $NONY :  4A DELIVERY CODE
     F*   "   $INVN : 20A INVOICE#
     F*   OUT $MANI : 20A MANIFEST#
     F*       $RTN  :  1A RETURN FLAG (BLANK=OK, *=ERROR)
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PL19FIF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
     C           KEY1      SETLLAB#PL19F
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           KEY1      READEAB#PL19F                 98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           BASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           BAEDIK    ORNE 'E'
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           BAPGID    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     MOVELBAPGID    LTR14  14 P
     C                     MOVELBANUKE    LTR2    2
     C                     MOVE LTR2      LTR14
     C                     MOVELLTR14     $MANI     P
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           $MANI     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE '*'       $RTN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *=============================================================
      *                    INITIAL PROCESS
      *=============================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $NONY   4
     C                     PARM           $INVN  20
     C                     PARM           $MANI  20
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K#NONY  40
     C                     KFLD           K#INVN 16
      *
     C                     MOVEL$NONY     K#NONY
     C                     MOVEL$INVN     K#INVN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $MANI
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $RTN
      *
     C                     ENDSR
